{"tid":1697354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府截至十月底，斥資超過一千萬維修受破壞的公共設施","createTime":"2019-11-06T20:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T01:05:14.000Z","uid":254923,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"cd7c2bc2c50c0cbda2a045868f38739d17c8860f","tid":1697354,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T20:50:23.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府指截至十月底，斥資超過一千萬維修或重置在反修例示威中受破壞的公共設施。<br />\n<br />\n運輸及房屋局回應立法會書面質詢時指，截至星期二，累計有145個港鐵或輕鐵車站設施受破壞，全港有約460組交通燈受到破壞或干擾、45公里的欄杆被拆除、遺失超過900個膠欄以及1500個水馬；食環署有670個垃圾桶被破壞。<br />\n<br />\n由六月至今，康文署轄下的康樂場地受遊行示威影響，臨時關閉超過1900次；路政署及食環署分別使用超過1000萬及56萬，維修或重置設施。"},{"pid":"2d6c3f267428c6119d1483035bddc1e0d9f40460","tid":1697354,"uid":254923,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T20:50:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母立法會就3千萬定成億，依家我哋搞撚左成五個月就1千萬都未到</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64fa1edecde2d005f3300fb1a5539cdf413913d","tid":1697354,"uid":254923,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T20:51:32.000Z","msg":"元朗天橋都17億啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14704798d5c6678e34e0c179165b635d99bf499e","tid":1697354,"uid":254923,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T20:52:07.000Z","msg":"高鐵定嗰條唔知乜撚嘢大橋更加唔使講<br />\n水泥錢都唔止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e417558dce68c4f56414e719e4ce154cc022a2e","tid":1697354,"uid":254923,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T21:03:55.000Z","msg":"死傻閪又凌晨開po邊撚個理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf02de65c5821721b98b40a8256f903420a5a192","tid":1697354,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T21:06:56.000Z","msg":"仲要係趕 先燒到呢個價 平時閒日 點燒"},{"pid":"402dbe933289165da0e6b190cf3b8cd6c7edb984","tid":1697354,"uid":129848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"ci